Permanently adds 3 Agility and 2 mastery to shoulder armor.

Can only be applied to your own armor, and doing so will cause it to become soulbound

Can only be applied to your own armor, and doing so will cause it to become soulbound

description:

Can only be applied to your own armor, and doing so will cause it to become soulbound. Cannot be applied to items higher than level 50

name: Master's Inscription of the Pinnacle

Can only be applied to your own armor, and doing so will cause it to become soulbound. Cannot be applied to items higher than level 50

name: Master's Inscription of the Storm

Can only be applied to your own armor, and doing so will cause it to become soulbound. Cannot be applied to items higher than level 50

name: Master's Inscription of the Crag

Can only be applied to your own armor, and doing so will cause it to become soulbound. Cannot be applied to items higher than level 50
